    <title>ubuntu qq、微信 安装及配置</title>
    <link href="https://blog.solarzhcl.com/2018/07/29/ubuntu-qq-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>https://blog.solarzhcl.com/2018/07/29/ubuntu-qq-安装及配置/</id>
    <published>2018-07-29T08:19:53.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-07-29T08:57:12.745Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>安装方法参考：<a href="https://www.lulinux.com/archives/1319" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deepin wine QQ</a></p><a id="more"></a><hr><p>下载安装包安装。</p><p>1.下载安装deepin-wine环境<br>链接：<a href="https://gitee.com/wszqkzqk/deepin-wine-for-ubuntu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://gitee.com/wszqkzqk/deepin-wine-for-ubuntu</a><br>2.安装相应容器：<br>链接：<a href="http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/</a></p><ul><li><a href="http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin.com.qq.office/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TIM</a></li><li><a href="http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin.com.qq.im/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">QQ</a></li><li><a href="http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin.com.qq.im/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">微信</a></li></ul><p>TIM默认图标文件像素比较低，在 <code>.desktop</code>文件中更换图标:</p><p><img src="/assets/pic/qq.png" alt="img"></p><h3 id="设置消息通知"><a href="#设置消息通知" class="headerlink" title="设置消息通知"></a>设置消息通知</h3><p>利用<code>notify-send</code> 和 <code>inotify-tools</code> 两个工具，监听qq消息声音文件的读取<br>创建脚本文件<code>qq-notify.sh</code>:</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#!/bin/bash</span></span><br><span class="line">file=<span class="string">"/home/XXX/.deepinwine/Deepin-TIM/drive_c/Program Files/Tencent/TIM/Misc/Sound/Classic/msg.wav"</span></span><br><span class="line">inotifywait -mq -e open <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$file</span>"</span> | <span class="keyword">while</span> <span class="built_in">read</span> event</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">do</span></span><br><span class="line">notify-send -i <span class="string">"/home/solar/图片/qq.png"</span> <span class="string">'XXX'</span> <span class="string">'收到一条QQ消息'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">done</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将脚本文件添加到开机启动</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;安装方法参考：&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lulinux.com/archives/1319&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Deepin wine QQ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
